films.title: The Story of Jesus for Children
films.description: In the first century, a group of children meet together to talk about what they've seen and heard about Jesus. Some believe Jesus is the Son of God. But others think Jesus may just be tricking the people.

films.title: JESUS
films.description: Jesus constantly surprises and confounds people, from His miraculous birth to His rise from the grave. Follow His life through excerpts from the Book of Luke, all the miracles, the teachings, and the passion.

films.title: Magdalena - Director's Cut
films.description: Magdalena, a film made especially for women, beautifully shares God's love and the gospel, engaging women at the heart level with the potential of changing their lives for eternity. The Director's Cut is 82 minutes and includes additional scenes.
